es!!\\r\\nHim: I can and I will....bloody foreigners!\\r\\nI raised my voice, Go...just bugger off you ignorant excuse of a human being,  the young man said thank you and again that he was sorry and wheeled his bike away.....the older guy started to walk off...but was still ranting about foreigners....I told him if I saw an officer in the high street I would report him, at which he stopped shouting.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"Eve Taylor\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-01T12:00:32.078Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-01T12:37:14.296Z\",\"support\":null},{\"id\":52,\"lat\":\"50.659079\",\"lng\":\"-1.149397\",\"time\":\"2016-06-25T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Sandown\",\"description\":\"Got verbal abuse for voting Remain. Repeated shouting by one individual \\\"You traitor to the fucking race!\\\" and \\\"Fuck You!\\\"\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Isle of Wight\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-01T12:05:53.663Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-01T12:37:24.599Z\",\"support\":null},{\"id\":53,\"lat\":\"55.843685\",\"lng\":\"-4.268446\",\"time\":\"2016-06-30T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Maxwell Road\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Glasgow\",\"description\":\"Man stood in group preparing for a March outside Orange and Purple Lodge Building shouts \\\"fuck off back home to Poland\\\" at young man.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"G41 1QP\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Glasgow City\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-01T12:06:54.790Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-01T12:37:30.322Z\",\"support\":null},{\"id\":54,\"lat\":\"51.515212\",\"lng\":\"-0.141837\",\"time\":\"2016-06-25T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Oxford Street\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London\",\"description\":\"Whilst queuing to e