ng Indian.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"OX1 1HS\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Oxfordshire\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-05T08:34:42.307Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-05T09:23:52.714Z\",\"support\":\"It was about 9pm in the evening, there were not many people around, and no one spoke up or offered support.\"},{\"id\":123,\"lat\":\"51.590219\",\"lng\":\"-0.139372\",\"time\":\"2016-07-01T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London Borough of Haringey\",\"description\":\"Yesterday 1 July 2016 I boarded the 134 bus towards North Finchley outside Highgate tube station and witnessed a racist verbal attack towards a European couple (not sure where they were from).  I sat downstairs in the back and was facing the back row and a middle aged white English man who was mumbling to himself.  At first I ignored it as this happens often on buses in London but then I could hear him saying nasty things and after a few minutes of me sitting on the bus the man sitting next to me asked the English man what his problem was. I could only  imagine he'd been enduring his insults for a while now. Then the English man started yelling and tell him to 'f*ck off'. By this point the European man was agitated and told him to behave himself but the English man kept yelling and then when the European man asked who he thought he was talking to him like that, the English man yelled 'I am English and you can f*ck off'.  At this point most passengers including me told him to f*ck off and that he was a disgrace to this country. The English man kept yelling and European man's partner told him to calm down and luckily at that point we arrived at the top of Muswell Hill where most of the passengers (including the couple) got off. The English man stayed in the back seat whilst the passengers left on the bus (including myself) went to sit far away from him.  Shortly after this another man went over to congratulate the English man for sticking up for 'us'. This was horrible to say the least. I couldn't contain myself and told him to 'f*ck off' as well.  He didn't respond to me and luckily for me a very nice lady calmed me down. Needless to say I was very angry and shaken. I've lived in Muswell Hill for two years and this has never happened on this bus route.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"N10\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-02T19:15:55.311Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T01:00:22.891Z\",\"support\":\"Yes as mentioned above many of the passengers defended the European man and told the English man he was a disgrace to this country.  \"},{\"id\":138,\"lat\":\"52.443155\",\"lng\":\"-1.829907\",\"time\":\"2016-06-29T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Birmingham\",\"description\":\"Driving car stopped and threw water bottles and abuse at Muslim couple having a walk\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"West Midlands\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T01:23:45.348Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T01:25:16.308Z\",\"support\":\"\"},{\"id\":140,\"lat\":\"52.636878\",\"lng\":\"-1.139759\",\"time\":\"2016-06-26T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Leicester\",\"description\":\"A Ugandan man had a banana thrown at him outside his children's school in a racially motivated attack.\\r\\n\\\"A car stopped alongside me going in the opposite direction.\\r\\n\\\"I looked to my side and saw this man in the driver's seat. The man, who was white, looked at me and seemed to be very angry.\\r\\n\\\"His window was down and he threw a banana at me. My window was closed so the banana just fell to the road.\\r\\n\\\"I began to drive off slowly. I could hear him shouting but could not make out the words.\\r\\n\\\"I was very upset. My 10-yea