y were about to leave one of them turned and saw me, and called me a \\\"dirty bitch\\\" out of the blue and walked off. \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"SE11 6NH\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T10:10:00.387Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T11:04:43.432Z\",\"support\":\"No one else was around, apart from her friend who laughed. \"},{\"id\":173,\"lat\":\"52.636878\",\"lng\":\"-1.139759\",\"time\":\"2016-07-01T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Leicester\",\"description\":\"ADT Cabs in Leicester City - Driver refused to pick up owner with his guide dog - clearly breaking the law and discriminatory \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":false,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Leicester\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T14:54:22.642Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T14:54:22.642Z\",\"support\":\"Only the owner https://www.facebook.com/jessica.amy.g/videos/636291893217728/\"},{\"id\":177,\"lat\":\"50.340378\",\"lng\":\"-4.783425\",\"time\":\"2016-06-01T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Saint Austell\",\"description\":\"In work was told by a person that there are too many immigrants in the country and they had voted out because of it. They stated they were proud to be a racist.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Cornwall\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T16:03:25.746Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T16:46:21.856Z\",\"support\":\"I told them I was a migrant and it was people like me that they were voting out. I was helping a family member of theirs at the time. \"},{\"id\":180,\"lat\":\"51.79929\",\"lng\":\"-0.201873\",\"time\":\"2016-07-25T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Welwyn Garden City\",\"description\":\"Both my children were told to \\\"go home, and leave this country\\\" by a woman on a bus as they travelled home from school. My children are of a mixed heritage, mother is from Kenya and I am also of mixed heritage of English and Kashmir, but both kids are UK citizens born in London and Hertfordshire and have always lived here.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Hertfordshire\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T18:15:02.530Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T18:17:50.116Z\",\"support\":\"No one offered them any support, with several other adult passengers laughing at them and pointing.\"},{\"id\":151,\"lat\":\"52.2257\",\"lng\":\"-2.742772\",\"time\":\"2016-06-25T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Leominster\",\"description\":\"Two days after the referendum (Saturday) my husband was walking alone through a small park in Leominster on his way to the train station from work at about 7.30pm.  A group of lads at the skate park shouted at him: 'Go home black bastard', 'he's a paki', 'he's a nigger', 'we're in control now'.  He walked faster as he was out-numbered and afraid.  The incident has been reported to the police, who came round to our house two days later and took a statement and said the local team would be taking it up.  The very helpful officer thought there would be little chance of a conviction for hate crime unless there had been witnesses or CCTV.  \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Herefordshire\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T09:27:58.506Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T09:44:59.788Z\",\"support\":\"There was no-one else close enough to the incident to hear what was going on.  My husband's work colleagues are supportive.  Some of them are Polish and are very worried for their security. The police have been very supportive, and one of the local county councillors has written a letter to the local newspaper condemning racism wholeheartedly.  We have had no reply from our MP Jesse Norman.  \"},{\"id\":152,\"lat\":\"51.477796\",\"lng\":\"-3.177594\",\"time\":\"2016-06-25T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Saint Mary Street\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Cardiff\",\"description\":\"Boys in a bar told me \\\"you look a bit European, when are you fucking off back to Europe\\\"\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Cardiff\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"H\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T10:05:47.183Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T11:04:16.523Z\",\"support\":\"No one but they were kicked out of the bar shortly after this for being loud\"},{\"id\":155,\"lat\":\"51.781858\",\"lng\":\"-2.576528\",\"time\":\"2016-07-03T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Forest of Dean District\",\"description\":\"This morning my neighbour after a diatribe of anti europe stuff said \\\"we can't even deport the rapist muslims, these muslims are taking our jobs, Syria is where I want to go because it's empty now, they are all coming here and taking what's ours\\\" \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Gloucestershire\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T10:42:41.997Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T11:05:47.049Z\",\"support\":\"\\r\\nI spoke up against scapegoating and tried to explain it in a calm way\"},{\"id\":156,\"lat\":\"53.36063\",\"lng\":\"-1.470657\",\"time\":\"2016-07-02T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Well Road\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Sheffield\",\"description\":\"Asian lady complaining that teenage girl who had run into a pub, clearly hiding, had been throwing stones at her house.  Large group of men shouting back harassing the lady \\\"We're all Brexit aren't we\\\", and \\\"how did you vote, love?\\\"\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"S8 9TZ\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"South Yorkshire\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T10:47:40.654Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T11:06:40.786Z\",\"support\":\"Pub staff offered support to the lady\"},{\"id\":167,\"lat\":\"51.497495\",\"lng\":\"-0.135658\",\"time\":\"2016-06-23T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"City of Westminster\",\"description\":\"Don't take this the wrong way, please. I am one of those people they call an 'ex-pat', living on my old age pension in France. Britain just had a referendum but I was not allowed to vote because I have been living here over 15 years. I can only assume that was because I am now regarded as friends with those naughty foreign French people, even though the results of that referendum now threaten my very survival since I suffer from a long term illness which requires regular medical treatment and there is a danger of my medical cover being withdrawn if the UK does exit. My partner is a Swiss lady so she would then be unable to come with me to the UK because of restrictions on 'immigration'. She will be 76, and I will be 72  this month. I accuse a certain N.Farage of racism in this case.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":false,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T13:17:36.373Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T13:17:36.373Z\",\"support\":\"Even the British high court refused to help me and others in similar situations.\"},{\"id\":168,\"lat\":null,\"lng\":null,\"time\":\"2016-06-29T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"23 Queen Square\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London\",\"description\":\"A patient in an NHS hospital refused to be seen by a consultant colleague from Italy, citing the referendum result.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"WC 1N 3BG\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T13:55:01.593Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T16:49:41.707Z\",\"support\":\"Several colleagues spoke up.\"},{\"id\":163,\"lat\":\"51.375801\",\"lng\":\"-2.359904\",\"time\":\"2016-07-01T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Bath\",\"description\":\"A note was put through my work door, it stated how disgusting it was that my company hired me, a foreign person though I have lived in the UK for 20 years. I am American and not from the EU.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Bath and North East Somerset\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T12:29:39.053Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T16:52:17.888Z\",\"support\":\"No, my company is supporting and standing by me, it was placed anonymously in my store.\"},{\"id\":162,\"lat\":\"51.015344\",\"lng\":\"-3.106849\",\"time\":\"2016-06-29T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Taunton Deane District\",\"description\":\"Child in my class aged 10 told German student teacher \\\"I'm not doing what a bloody foreigner tells me to\\\". \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Somerset\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T12:26:30.034Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T16:52:44.449Z\",\"support\":\"Dealt with by senior management.  Student excluded. \"},{\"id\":161,\"lat\":\"54.978252\",\"lng\":\"-1.61778\",\"time\":\"2016-06-24T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Davy Bank\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Newcastle upon Tyne\",\"description\":\"I was at work chatting about how the media has misled people about refugees and one of my supervisors said the refugees were rats and should be shot at our border until they turn back. Then I got in a heated argument about dehumanizing a minority group and that it was racism.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"NE28\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Tyne and Wear\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T12:09:32.980Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T16:53:43.962Z\",\"support\":\"Nope except my other supervisor joined in to add that he believed we should get all the refugees on a bout in the channel then sink it. I had to explain to them that they could lose their jobs if I made a formal complaint which shut them up for the time.\"},{\"id\":157,\"lat\":\"51.503381\",\"lng\":\"-0.061374\",\"time\":\"2016-07-01T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Wapping High Street\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London\",\"description\":\"On the 100 bus in Wapping around 6pm on Friday, July 1:\\r\\n- Three folks across from and to the right of me loudly having a conversation across the aisle in a russian-related language (not sure which one, and that's my bad). \\r\\n- Me, annoyed at the volume, but engrossed in my phone and not reacting\\r\\n- Older white guy to my left who is obviously annoyed at something, but otherwise silent until...\\r\\n\\r\\n...just before the Wapping Health Center bus stop, older white guy bursts out with \\\"FUCKING HELL! Speak English...\\\" (first part REALLY loud, second part nearly under his breath). Startled, I looked up to see him looking our direction, and clearly ask in my American accent, \\\"Is there a problem, sir?\\\"\\r\\n\\r\\n\\\"No problem. *surprised look which quickly narrows into a squint* Why would you ask that?\\\"\\r\\n\\r\\n\\\"Well, most folks who don't have a problem don't suddenly burst out with obscenity, or make comments about the language others are speaking in.\\\"\\r\\n\\r\\n\\\"I don't have a problem. And even if I did, that's my business, innit? Mind your own business!\\\" and he fled off the bus to avoid further confrontation.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T11:05:53.143Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T11:07:26.021Z\",\"support\":\"I spoke up and confronted the bigot. He left to avoid further verbal confrontation. \"},{\"id\":159,\"lat\":\"55.857245\",\"lng\":\"-4.255306\",\"time\":\"2016-07-01T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Glasgow\",\"description\":\"My brother and I were walking by the bank machines outside the st enoch bank of scotland around 4pm on friday the 1st of july when suddenly two neds lunged at a mixed race man next to us.They called him a p*** and said he should go home as well as attempting to hit him with a bottle.My brother stepped in and made sure the guy was safe but the two guys went further down past the subway station and pointed/stared down other POC that walked by.We are both a quarter turkish and frightened that our dede(grandpa) could be harassed like this.Post-Brexit Britain is not somewhere I'm happy to live in.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"Glasgow City\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"Jessica Secmezsoy-Urquhart\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T12:01:25.342Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T16:45:01.104Z\",\"support\":\"My brother did but most people didnt which surprised me.My brother like me is autistic so I was scared the guys would maybe lash at him too but I was proud he did step in when no one else was doing so.We both told POC walking towards where they were to avoid them/stay safe.\"},{\"id\":160,\"lat\":\"55.953252\",\"lng\":\"-3.188267\",\"time\":\"2012-08-07T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"North bridge\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Edinburgh\",\"description\":\"While using ATM someone shouted ''Fucking Polish''\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Edinburgh\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T12:08:23.021Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T16:53:02.253Z\",\"support\":\"Nobody \"},{\"id\":171,\"lat\":\"53.480759\",\"lng\":\"-2.242631\",\"time\":\"2014-08-17T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Manchester\",\"description\":\"A Labour councillor Mark Hackett called me all sorts of racist and Islamophobic names in emails and made all sorts of mad accusations based on his interpretation of the spelling of my name and me helping Stop The War organize an event.  Manchester City Council found him guilty of breaking \\\"code of conduct\\\" but allowed him to retire without take any action.  Ms Liz Treacy the legal head of Manchester City Council refused to take my phone calls when I was being harassed.  Liz Treacy has now dragged out a supposed potential hearing for over two years and allowed Mark Hackett to walk away quietly.  Incidentally Stop The War Manchester staff did not offer me any help to try and get justice. And more than 2 years on I am still trying to get justice - the racist Manchester Police force has ignored this and indeed their Salford East GMP has harassed me when I made other complaints of anti-social behaviour that was taking place in the area.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":false,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater Manchester\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"Adnan Q\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T14:41:50.108Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T14:41:50.108Z\",\"support\":\"No one helped me but Islamic Human Rights Commission put a school leaver on the case and tried to take undue credit. Other organizations have also tried to take credit for him \\\"retiring\\\" and I find this so pessimistic - that there is a victim and the so called advocacy groups are either ignoring me or trying to falsely take credit for absolutely nothing.\"},{\"id\":158,\"lat\":\"54.971994\",\"lng\":\"-1.616569\",\"time\":\"2016-07-02T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Clayton Street\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Newcastle upon Tyne\",\"description\":\"A group of drunk men were chanting \\\"He's not English, she's not English\\\"\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"NE1 5PW\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Tyne and Wear\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T11:58:38.637Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T16:44:37.607Z\",\"support\":\"None.\"},{\"id\":178,\"lat\":\"52.75168\",\"lng\":\"0.402296\",\"time\":\"2016-06-28T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"King's Lynn and West Norfolk District\",\"description\":\"So for the first time in a long while I experienced a narrow minded racist in town this morning. Who told me now we've had the referendum all the immigrants should go home. To which I ignored at first till he followed me continuing to say it and tell me to go back to my own country with everyone starting to look and watch. To then get so angry and turn and shout at him that he's a narrow minded self obsessed little person with no idea of democracy and what voting out of the EU actually meant. I shouted at him that he should read the history books and actually find out some facts before shouting his mouth off in public just because he sees a foreigner. I angrily continued to shout that I was born and brought up here and this is my country as much as anyone else's who works and pays taxes and owns property. To then get claps from everyone watching the situation along with a community police officer. I've never been so angry, but also so proud to have actually done that out in the open and in front of so many people.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Norfolk\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T16:22:08.156Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T16:46:10.516Z\",\"support\":\"I spoke up\"},{\"id\":175,\"lat\":\"51.081397\",\"lng\":\"1.169456\",\"time\":\"2016-06-20T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Shepway District\",\"description\":\"Man on bus talking loudly about Brexit, while making it clear that he loves people of all creeds and colours, in a 'some of my best friends are black' kind of patronising manner. Then starts talking about the whinging Scottish and how they don't know when to shut up. Young girl who has been quietly listening to all this, answers her mobile phone, and it is clear she is Scottish. Scottish girl then challenges the anti-Scottish man who then denies he said anything. But he did.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Kent\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T15:28:33.219Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T16:47:10.049Z\",\"support\":\"No. \"},{\"id\":174,\"lat\":\"51.428289\",\"lng\":\"-0.102429\",\"time\":\"2016-07-03T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Knights Hill\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London Borough of Lambeth\",\"description\":\"Black British woman and white English man, shouting out racists comments near bus stop in West Norwood. Shouting that Europeans should go home directly in front of me and my family who are mixed family of Europeans and British. \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"SE27 0HY\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T15:25:16.444Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T16:47:23.899Z\",\"support\":\"No one said a word\"},{\"id\":172,\"lat\":\"50.834209\",\"lng\":\"-0.271556\",\"time\":\"2016-06-17T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Weald Dyke \",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Shoreham by Sea    Adur District\",\"description\":\"a cruel,  highly racist entire row of home-made posters in a UKIP supporters front garden, abutting the street so it could not not be seen by anyone passing by to and from the beach. I spoke to several folk who were very upset.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"bn \",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"West Sussex\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T14:49:56.655Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T16:48:20.144Z\",\"support\":\" Someone put a polite but firm notice on top of one of the posters saying how appallingly racist they were and how ashamed it made people here feel.\\r\\nIt was reported to the police.\\r\\nThey were all removed from the garden. \"},{\"id\":170,\"lat\":\"51.507351\",\"lng\":\"-0.127758\",\"time\":\"2016-06-23T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Chalk Farm Road/ Kentish Town Area\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London\",\"description\":\"Landlord calls tenants in the morning after the night of the referendum (Romanian tenants who were sharing a house, one of whom is a pharmacist with a well known high street chemist) to  warn them with obvious hostility in his voice that they have to vacate his property as soon as possible. On being asked why the big haste as the tenancy agreement did not yet expire and they seemed to get along well for many years as well as always paying the rent in time they were told that he doesn't want to rent his property to immigrants anymore.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"N2\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T14:41:25.910Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T16:49:13.822Z\",\"support\":\"Friends and acquaintances have been informed and asked for help.\"},{\"id\":169,\"lat\":\"52.056736\",\"lng\":\"1.14822\",\"time\":\"2016-06-30T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Ipswich\",\"description\":\"Waiting to get on a bus a man said congratulations you are the first English voice I've hear all day. I said I love the diversity don't you? He said I'm trying to wonder where 'they' all come from. I said probably here maybe second or third generation and isn't wonderful to have the gift of being multi lingual. He shut up then.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Suffolk\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T13:58:36.423Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T16:49:29.476Z\",\"support\":\"I spoke up in a polite a way as possible to make my point. \"},{\"id\":164,\"lat\":\"51.513162\",\"lng\":\"-0.088338\",\"time\":\"2016-06-13T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London\",\"description\":\"On the westbound Central Line in London on the 13th June around 6pm my friends and I were travelling towards Soho for the Orlando vigil. A woman of colour was stood next to us. An elderly white man asked her if the train went to Holborn. When the woman said \\\"Pardon?\\\" as she had not heard him, he repeated it slowly, loudly, and patronisingly as if to make the point that she couldn't speak English. He continued to harass her. When a friend of mine asked him if he would like to sit down to get him away from the woman, he directed his rant towards us (visibly members of the LGBT community) shouting amongst other things about how we were \\\"riffraff\\\" and ought to be \\\"burnt\\\".\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T12:55:34.760Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T16:51:53.485Z\",\"support\":\"When the woman was being harassed, I offered her my seat (to get her away from the man) and my friend offered the man a seat for the same reason. When he turned his attentions to us, no-one did anything.\"},{\"id\":179,\"lat\":\"51.60197\",\"lng\":\"-0.05391\",\"time\":\"2016-07-02T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London\",\"description\":\"I have been told to fuck off from this country by a black man\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"N17\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"Yuksel Ozkaya\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T18:00:33.468Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T18:18:17.243Z\",\"support\":\"\"},{\"id\":181,\"lat\":\"51.605984\",\"lng\":\"0.057462\",\"time\":\"2016-06-23T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Chigwell road\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London Borough of Redbridge\",\"description\":\"Racist abuse last 3yrs from  next door neighbour. \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"Ig88bl\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"Rashid\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T18:22:29.636Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T18:24:31.783Z\",\"support\":\"No \"},{\"id\":182,\"lat\":\"54.540308\",\"lng\":\"-1.293636\",\"time\":\"2016-07-02T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Westbury street\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Thornaby\",\"description\":\"I am a PhD student at Durham University, Queens Campus, Stockton-on-Tees. I am an international student from India. I currently live in Thornaby. \\r\\nOn Saturday 2nd July  2016 at 8:30am, I went out to buy milk from nearby Saiinsbury's (Westbury street). While heading home, I felt a heavy and painful punch on my back. I must have stopped breathing for few seconds and when I turned around, there was well-built drunk man staring at me angrily. He asked me about my birth place but I couldn't speak. He then told me that \\\"What the f*ck are you doing here...Go back to your country\\\". I was shaking and confused as this was the first I encountered a physical violence. He then crossed the street and went inside one of the back alleys. I kept walking home and started sobbing. I felt like my birth was a big mistake and I shouldn't exist according to the theory of natural selection.\\r\\nIt's been 6 and a half years, I never encountered such an incident personally. I dedicated my whole University life in the UK and being a self-funded student I have enormous pressure to achieve my academic goals.\\r\\nThis incident happened on Westbury street, Thornaby, nearby the Sainsbury's. And my house is few blocks away from where it happened. \\r\\nThe man was probably 6' tall, broad shouldered and shaved head.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"TS17 6NE\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Stockton-on-Tees\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"Mohit Jain\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T18:40:43.039Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T18:44:27.039Z\",\"support\":\"There was an old couple standing at the bus stop nearby who saw the whole incident. They made sure I was okay after the man crossed the street (which was really nice of them).\"},{\"id\":184,\"lat\":\"53.683298\",\"lng\":\"-1.505924\",\"time\":\"2016-06-28T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Batley Road\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Wakefield District\",\"description\":\"First a man leaned out of his car, made an obscene gesture and told me to f*** off. Then 15 minutes later a man told me to 'Get back where I came from'\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"West Yorkshire\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T19:30:42.681Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T19:32:02.181Z\",\"support\":\"Nobody spoke up or offered support\"},{\"id\":186,\"lat\":\"51.561145\",\"lng\":\"-0.108864\",\"time\":\"2016-06-29T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Isledon Road\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London\",\"description\":\"My partner (he's 64 and white British) told me this: he was at a bus stop on the way to a hospital appointment. Another white man aged about 50, and drinking cider, was also there. A black woman aged about 65 came out of the nearby doctor's surgery and sat at the bus stop. The cider drinker leaned over and called the woman an f***ing black c***.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"N7 7JP\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T22:19:44.072Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T22:34:13.798Z\",\"support\":\"My partner told the man he was being racist and threatened to call the police. The man stopped and my partner \\u0026 the woman got on their bus.\"},{\"id\":187,\"lat\":\"53.800755\",\"lng\":\"-1.549077\",\"time\":\"2016-06-28T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Harehilla\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"City of Leeds\",\"description\":\"On the 42 bus to Leeds city centre when two teenagers were getting on the bus. There was two ladies with babies in front of them, they were not speaking English. The teens started to spew hate about them and that they should go home. \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"West Yorkshire\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T22:31:53.422Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T22:34:31.674Z\",\"support\":\"I was shocked - happened to fast to say anything to them. \"},{\"id\":188,\"lat\":null,\"lng\":null,\"time\":\"2016-07-04T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Kings Road\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Brighton\",\"description\":\"I was cycling westwards on Brighton sea-front cycle lane at slower than walking speed to allow an oncoming runner and cyclist pass safely.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe white male runner passing me in the opposite direction deliberately jabbed his elbow hard into my upper arm. He didn't speak or look at me before or after the incident.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"BN2 3AF\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"East Sussex\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-04T09:47:05.596Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-04T10:11:57.247Z\",\"support\":\"\"},{\"id\":189,\"lat\":\"51.548156\",\"lng\":\"-0.075671\",\"time\":\"2016-06-02T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London\",\"description\":\"A white man outside a shop shouting aggressively at a black man inside, calling him a \\\"fucking n***er\\\". \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-04T10:31:24.784Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-04T10:52:08.137Z\",\"support\":\"Not as far as I know\"},{\"id\":190,\"lat\":\"51.525207\",\"lng\":\"-2.603881\",\"time\":\"2016-06-30T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Bristol\",\"description\":\"My brother was parking in the car park when he saw a black woman being abused in her car by a white pedestrian. Called her a nigger among other things and proceeded to threaten a young (17 year old or so) black gentleman who tried to tell him his language was out of order. \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"Bs34 5dg\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"South Gloucestershire\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"Leigh McKenna \",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-04T11:35:00.418Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-04T12:40:26.930Z\",\"support\":\"A black teenager spoke up (and was threatened) and eventually my (15 stone) brother interjected and the altercation fizzled out.\"},{\"id\":191,\"lat\":null,\"lng\":null,\"time\":\"2016-07-03T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\" Willesden Green High Street x St Pauls Avenue (in front of Sainbury's crossing)\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London\",\"description\":\"I needed to stop my car suddenly as the red light came up and waited a pedestrian that was crossing the street... My red light was still on but some people not really happy of me waiting started shouting and I tried to reply: _I'm waiting the green light and then came\\r\\n-FUCKING IMMIGRANT...\\r\\n\\r\\nI was so shocked that I couldn't remember to take note of his plate\\r\\n\\r\\nThat happened in Willesden Green High Street x St Pauls Avenue (in front of Sainbury's crossing)\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"NW2 BRENT\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"BRENT\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"Julia Penido\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-04T11:42:55.221Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-04T12:40:44.898Z\",\"support\":\"nope\"},{\"id\":194,\"lat\":\"56.116523\",\"lng\":\"-3.936903\",\"time\":\"2016-06-24T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Various\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Stirling\",\"description\":\"I have received several comments about being English (in Scotland). \\r\\n\\r\\nPeople chanting at me in a pub to \\\"fuck off home\\\"\\r\\n\\r\\nSomeone threw a beer can at me in a park on another occasion\\r\\n\\r\\nOn a third occasion my car was vandalised\\r\\n\\r\\nOn a fourth, well before Brexit, there was graffiti daubed on my front door\\r\\n\\r\\nI have only put the date of the first one as it doesn't allow you to put more than one date.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":false,\"postcode\":\"FK7 7JZ\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Stirling\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-04T16:04:40.027Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-04T16:04:40.027Z\",\"support\":\"No\"},{\"id\":193,\"lat\":\"51.604967\",\"lng\":\"-0.072279\",\"time\":\"2016-07-04T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Scotland Green\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London Borough of Haringey\",\"description\":\"I have been finding Islamophobic stickers on lamp posts and street signs all around Hartington Park in Tottenham, and up and down streets in the surrounding area. Most of them are in English, some of them are in Polish. When I see them I scrape them off, and over the last three month I have must scraped off at least thirty or forty, and that's just in a very small area. Just today I found a bunch of new ones that read \\\"FUCK ISLAM\\\" in huge letters, and in small letters \\\"Stop the Islamisation of Europe\\\" and \\\"Europe Wake Up\\\". Keep an eye out for this in your area, as most people don't think to look at lamp posts.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"N17\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-04T15:55:51.765Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-04T16:25:48.896Z\",\"support\":\"Most people don't know these stickers are even there. A few of them have already been half scraped off so you know some people are seeing them. I use a dog-tag to scrape them off, so carry something similar if you want to battle this  racist propaganda.\"},{\"id\":195,\"lat\":\"52.539611\",\"lng\":\"-0.263173\",\"time\":\"2016-06-29T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"The Serpentine\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Peterborough\",\"description\":\"At a deli counter in Tescos Extra in Peterborough, customer remarks to counter operative \\\"Aren't you Polish, shouldn't you be going home?\\\"\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"PE7 8DR\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Peterborough\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"James\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-04T16:08:31.139Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-04T16:27:01.050Z\",\"support\":\"No\"},{\"id\":196,\"lat\":\"51.545927\",\"lng\":\"0.707712\",\"time\":\"2016-07-04T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"London road\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Southend-on-Sea\",\"description\":\"A man his 30s flashed his car to let me go ahead but as soon as I passed him he shouted at my through my window. I believe he saw that I was Asian and this aggravated him. I was with my children. My right ear hurts and I am scared. I raised my hand to thank him but he still shouted in an aggressive tone \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"Ss9 3nf\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Southend-on-Sea\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-04T17:39:38.086Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-04T17:41:03.458Z\",\"support\":\"\"},{\"id\":197,\"lat\":\"51.475348\",\"lng\":\"-0.040456\",\"time\":\"2016-07-04T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"New Cross Road\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London\",\"description\":\"One (white) man was squaring up to another (Asian) man on the Overground train... \\\"I will fucking punch you\\\" etc. etc. The victim here is ignoring the shouts, until eventually the offender shouts \\\"Piss off back to your country, Brownie\\\"\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"SE14 6AR\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"Phoebe Bunting\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-04T18:32:47.087Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-04T18:39:49.284Z\",\"support\":\"Thankfully, myself and a few other commuters turned around in defence of this poor man. \\\"What the hell did you just say?\\\" \\\"This is the country we are all in right now therefore it's all our country\\\" \\\"if you don't like that, I suggest you fuck off, you racist moron\\\". We all asked the white \\\"gentleman\\\" to leave the train at New Cross Gate once it had stopped, which he did (but very angrily). \\r\\n\\r\\nI asked the victim if he was OK... he replied,\\\"I think so. But that has never happened to me before, my whole life in London\\\".\"},{\"id\":198,\"lat\":\"51.29631\",\"lng\":\"-0.755945\",\"time\":\"2016-07-04T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Farnborough\",\"description\":\"'White zone' sticker on Farnborough Main station bus shelter.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"Hampshire\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"Emma Dermott\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-04T18:42:16.258Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-04T21:18:14.526Z\",\"support\":\"Yes, another woman took pictures and helped me peel it off. Have reported it to the council.\"},{\"id\":199,\"lat\":\"51.891734\",\"lng\":\"0.815238\",\"time\":\"2016-06-28T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Dugard avenue \",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Borough of Colchester\",\"description\":\"My mum an 81 year old Chinese lady in uk since 1964 was racially abused in the street by a teenager in Gang of Four teenage boys who told her she had to leave and why was she still here because of the EU out vote, it was very threatening to her.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"CO3 \",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Essex\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"The victims daughter \",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-05T07:01:21.225Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-05T07:46:20.327Z\",\"support\":\"A middle aged man was in hearing distance and told her to ignore them but didn't challenge them himself\"},{\"id\":200,\"lat\":\"53.002668\",\"lng\":\"-2.179404\",\"time\":\"2016-06-25T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Stoke-on-Trent\",\"description\":\"Being told to go back home after the eu referendum\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Stoke-on-Trent\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-05T08:34:14.616Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-05T09:23:39.112Z\",\"support\":\"No\"},{\"id\":202,\"lat\":\"51.586505\",\"lng\":\"-0.306821\",\"time\":\"2016-07-02T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Kenton Road\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Haggerston\",\"description\":\"Man aggressively shouted at me that I didn't speak English. Then started telling me to fuck off.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"E9\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-05T08:43:51.776Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-05T09:24:06.465Z\",\"support\":\"No\"},{\"id\":205,\"lat\":null,\"lng\":null,\"time\":\"2016-06-27T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Kettering Road\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Northampton\",\"description\":\"My wife came across two elderly white men yelling at a young Muslim woman (20s, wearing hijab, with 2 children in tow), telling her to \\\"Go back to where she was born,\\\" etc. This took place in a supermarket! \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"NN3 6AA\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-05T08:58:47.952Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-05T09:25:08.103Z\",\"support\":\"My wife intervened, told the two elderly men that their attitude 