d 'English' - I'm therefore a racist. Sarcastically clapping their hands saying 'well done'. I simply tried to say it wasn't true and they don't know me so shouldn't assume anything. I was told I'm a majority white so gotta suck it up. This was the day after the referendum and I didn't want to reply further and fuel their anger. I was so badly tempted to be angry back but what would that achieve?\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":false,\"postcode\":\"SW1W 9SZ\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"Lee\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-06T22:04:13.172Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-06T22:04:13.172Z\",\"support\":\"Everyone else in the lift pretended to be on their phones or read their papers. \"},{\"id\":241,\"lat\":\"51.491141\",\"lng\":\"-0.226141\",\"time\":\"2016-07-01T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Bayonne park\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London\",\"description\":\"My husband and son went to play football at a playground near our home. We are french and a young black boy (11 to 13) told them \\\"fucking french, go back home\\\". This happened on two occasions on Friday 1st July and Sunday 2nd July.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"W8\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"Caroline Dubecq\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-06T19:32:22.181Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-06T22:50:51.956Z\",\"support\":\"\"},{\"id\":246,\"lat\":\"51.508472\",\"lng\":\"-0.128248\",\"time\":\"2016-06-25T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Trafalgar Square\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London\",\"description\":\"I was verbally assaulted by a drunk woman at pride festival. She came over when she saw me offering my umbrella shelter to her friend and pointed at me. She then went on to say \\\"We voted out of the EU to get rid of people like you\\\". \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email