e country. Then the man at the front said \\\"years ago Hitler tried to kill everyone like you and I can see why\\\". \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"GL1 4JJ\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Gloucestershire\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"Graeme Thorne \",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-13T15:19:23.457Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-13T16:02:03.397Z\",\"support\":\"Nobody said anything against the racism except for the school children who were supporting their peer. I wish I had spoken up but the man at the front was incredibly threatening. He looked a bit like the comedian Rich Hall, but skinnier and dirtier. \"},{\"id\":278,\"lat\":\"50.726519\",\"lng\":\"-1.864899\",\"time\":\"2016-06-24T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Bournemouth\",\"description\":\"Went to Asda day after referendum. Was told by 2 teenage boys, approx age 13-14  \\\" Oy, mate, this is England, it's OUR England now\\\"...adult male with them just watched and laughed.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"BH8 8DL\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Bournemouth\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"Pedro Rozzi\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-13T16:36:27.609Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-13T18:55:36.539Z\",\"support\":\"\"},{\"id\":279,\"lat\":null,\"lng\":null,\"time\":\"2016-07-11T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"37 Shelfield Road\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Nelson\",\"description\":\"Someone said she will \\\"set our house on fire\\\" call me fucking Lithuanian cunt and silly cow, her 12 years old daughter said to my 8 year old girl \\\"Lithuanian bitch\\\".\\r\\n\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"BB9 8BY\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"Lancashire\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"Brigita\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-14T10:34:48.666Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-14T13:50:52.728Z\",\"support\":\"\"},{\"id\":280,\"lat\":\"55.975117\",\"lng\":\"-3.166243\",\"time\":\"2016-07-09T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null