ion\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"sanjay poonanthalam \",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-21T13:56:52.872Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T13:56:52.872Z\",\"support\":\"people around just looked and laughed \"},{\"id\":323,\"lat\":\"54.136878\",\"lng\":\"-1.523581\",\"time\":\"2016-07-04T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Market Place West\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Ripon\",\"description\":\"I was called turkroach and kebab lover in Greggs, they claimed it was just banter but even the staff were laughing. There's clearly institutional racism there, perhaps due to Harrogate not being very diverse. \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"HG4 1BW\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"North Yorkshire\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"Hüseyin Öztürk\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-21T13:25:53.224Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T23:38:26.233Z\",\"support\":\"No one, literally disgusted, they were all laughing or smirking. \"},{\"id\":325,\"lat\":\"54.978252\",\"lng\":\"-1.61778\",\"time\":\"2016-07-21T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Newcastle upon Tyne\",\"description\":\"i was in greggs getting a steak bake and someone called me a 'black bastard'\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Tyne and Wear\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-21T13:28:46.291Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T23:39:12.967Z\",\"support\":\"\"},{\"id\":353,\"lat\":null,\"lng\":null,\"time\":\"2010-11-01T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Leicester\",\"description\":\"I went to Benny's Chicken near the water fountain. I greeted the staff and made my order. The guy in charge told me the price, which wasn't the regular price. I confronted him saying that isn't the price, he just looked at me like a POS. He gave me tourist prices, so wrong. I always used the Benny's opposite CEX after that. I'm not sure if the prejudice was racial or religiously motivated.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":false,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-21T15:54:15.960Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T15:54:15.960Z\",\"support\":\"No.\"},{\"id\":364,\"lat\":\"51.428825\",\"lng\":\"-0.547876\",\"time\":\"2016-07-21T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Runnymede District\",\"description\":\"Recently moved to the area. Tracksuited youth of about 14 or 15 told me to \\\"go back to São Tomé and Príncipe\\\" before saying something along the lines of \\\"too many São Tomé and Príncipians are stealing our jobs\\\".\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"tw200rb \",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Surrey\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-21T18:35:49.891Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T23:32:12.400Z\",\"support\":\"No one helped, another old man in his garden also expressed his hatred of São Tomé and Príncipians\"},{\"id\":363,\"lat\":\"53.795984\",\"lng\":\"-1.759398\",\"time\":\"2016-07-06T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Thorncliffe Rd\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Bradford District\",\"description\":\"I was racially abused by anti-semites outside my local synagogue\\r\\nthe I was verbally attacked by a gang of middle eastern youths who called me all sorts of names like 'butcher' or 'vampire' or 'monster'\\r\\nI quickly tried to hurry past them as they spat at me and insulted me viciously when a car suddenly came out of nowhere and some racist goys started throwing bacon, chicken nuggets and prawns at us from their car window while yelling racist slogans like 'fuck off we're full' and 'this is our england'\\r\\nthe youths scattered at the sight of the bacon and since shellfish and pork products arent kosher I ended up having to crawl under a nearby mitsubishi verada sedan as it rained streaks of bacon and rotten prawns all around us\\r\\nat this point the youths seemed to have forgotten about me and decided to attack the car carrying the racists who then sped off with one of them pointing their arse out the window and taking a shit onto the street\\r\\nwhile the youths chased the car i quickly scuttled out from under my hiding place over the non-kosher prawns and ran to the Bradford Reform Synagogue where I had to be calmed down by my Rabbi\\r\\nI am absolutely appalled by this behaviour, I emigrated to the UK from Israel 20 years ago to set up my jewelers in Bradford and I am ashamed that the jewish community still has to suffer these racist attacks from bigots\\r\\nI voted leave in the Bremain referendum and I hang an EU flag from my front window right next to my Israeli flag I'm just as British as the next person and I demand to be treated fairly\\r\\nI only hope when the labour party gets back into power that they can fix all these racists and stop their attacks\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"West Yorkshire\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"Mr Zedekiah Schwarz\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-21T18:34:15.752Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T23:32:59.924Z\",\"support\":\"When I went to my Synagogue and told them about what happened my community members were all shocked and appalled at what I had just suffered and needless to say the jewish community in Bradford stands with the message of multiculturalism and diversity as it is the only way to defeat these racists\\r\\n\"},{\"id\":342,\"lat\":\"51.505785\",\"lng\":\"-0.43098\",\"time\":\"2016-07-20T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Dawley Road\",\"house\":\"1-3\",\"town\":\"Uxbridge\",\"description\":\"I am an orthodox Jewish man. Walking down a street in west London I was approached by a gang of what I can only describe as \\\"skinheads\\\", who accosted me abruptly with the words \\\"Hey Chaim, want some shekels, greedy Jew?\\\", with which they started throwing 1 \\u0026 2pence coins at the ground around me. I don't know how they guessed my name. I politely asked them to stop and tried to quickly move away but they followed me chanting \\\"oy vey, it's a shoah, the goyim know\\\". A shoah is a holocaust! I told them my grandfather perished in the holocaust and they chanted, quite loudly \\\"six million more, lock the gas chamber door\\\" over and over again. I was almost moved to tears by this.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"UB8 3JU\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-21T14:43:01.806Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T23:42:34.176Z\",\"support\":\"No one seemed to care, heads down as if to pretend it wasn't happening.\"},{\"id\":337,\"lat\":\"51.461305\",\"lng\":\"-0.303771\",\"time\":\"2016-06-25T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London Borough of Richmond upon Thames\",\"description\":\"I was at Peter Oliver Library, renewing my books, when two middle aged men walked up to me and said that this Library had been around since 1488 and that it was apart of British history and that I was insulting them being there as a foreigner. I've never experienced anything like this until after the Brexit. I don't feel safe anymore.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"Samaira\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-21T14:01:22.712Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T23:45:33.783Z\",\"support\":\"Yes, thankfully the librarian told them men to leave and offered to call the police for me.\"},{\"id\":341,\"lat\":\"51.49521\",\"lng\":\"-0.143898\",\"time\":\"2016-06-04T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Victoria Street\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London\",\"description\":\"I was told to get my \\\"Disgusting lefty ginger scouse a*** back oop norf\\\" (sic) when I visited London to attend an anti Brexit march. This happened at Victoria Station. I was carrying a banner with a pro EU slogan, my daughter was left in tears. Truly we are a country divided\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":false,\"postcode\":\"SW1E 5ND\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"Doris\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-21T14:38:23.958Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T14:38:23.958Z\",\"support\":\"Everyone  laughed apart from the foreign protesters I was with who obviously didn't understand. \"},{\"id\":345,\"lat\":\"53.407622\",\"lng\":\"-2.977313\",\"time\":\"2016-06-01T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Lime Street\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Liverpool\",\"description\":\"It was late at night and I was locking the doors of my synagogue when I turned around and heard in the distance \\\"we know\\\" I thought to myself what do they know? Then a rock hit me and it read on the side \\\"Im glad the 6 gorrilion suffocated\\\". \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"L1 1JD\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Merseyside\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-21T15:18:58.833Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T15:57:02.400Z\",\"support\":\"I told my friends at the synagogue and they suggested keep reinforcing the message of diversity to counter their hate. \"},{\"id\":354,\"lat\":null,\"lng\":null,\"time\":\"2010-05-03T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Leicester\",\"description\":\"Two young men called my mother a white bitch whilst she was shopping.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":false,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-21T15:58:54.086Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T15:58:54.086Z\",\"support\":\"People don't want trouble, so no.\"},{\"id\":365,\"lat\":\"54.611721\",\"lng\":\"-5.967399\",\"time\":\"2016-07-20T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Twaddell Avenue\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Belfast\",\"description\":\"I was walking down the street and two Irish Republicans in Celtic shirts  shouted at me to 'fuck off you Brit back across the water'.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":false,\"postcode\":\"BT13 3LG\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Belfast\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-21T19:00:25.617Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T19:00:25.617Z\",\"support\":\"No. \\r\\nTwo smokers outside the bookies laughed.\"},{\"id\":344,\"lat\":\"53.47404\",\"lng\":\"-2.24199\",\"time\":\"2016-06-09T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Manchester\",\"description\":\"I was walking down the street and I quickly noticed the air blow against the top of my head, I knew imidietly that my yarmulke had been stolen, I turned around and a tall man dressed as a green frog was laughing and shouting \\\" Oy vey you can't shut me down kike\\\". \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"Greater Manchester\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-21T15:05:27.991Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T23:41:44.262Z\",\"support\":\"People who were coming out the pub joined in and started chanting \\\"Oy vey\\\" over and over again.\"},{\"id\":343,\"lat\":\"52.468164\",\"lng\":\"-1.854315\",\"time\":\"2015-06-18T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Coventry Road\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Birmingham\",\"description\":\"Several times have I walked through the small heath area with a couple of freind of mine in both broad daylight and night and been told to \\\"fuck off and go to your own area\\\". It's not so bad near the larger supermarket chains, but the further you get into the highstreet the more racial abuse I get from several different communities. I have been refused service by one or two of the local store chains and now avoid the area completely. The vast majority, though not agreeing with the attackers do not seem to care too much about it.\\r\\nThis is a mostly MiddleEastern area and not all the communities are bad, but some are absolutley terrible and cross group racial incidents are extremely frequent.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"West Midlands\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-21T14:56:15.612Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T23:42:15.231Z\",\"support\":\"I have had one or two speak up, but only a few times over several minor incidents. Luckily only one has involved a physical altercation, with a boxcutter knife of which ended up with me having to run for my life. This incident was reported to police but I never felt it worth telling to anyone else since the suspects were caught in the end for a fatal stabbing some time later.\"},{\"id\":340,\"lat\":\"51.596482\",\"lng\":\"-0.108943\",\"time\":\"2016-07-13T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London Borough of Haringey\",\"description\":\"i was travelling on the 29 bus when a black man called me a \\\"turkroach\\\" and told me that there was a storm brewing and people would be removing kebabs like me very soon \\r\\n \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"mehmet ozturk\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-21T14:20:53.741Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T23:43:12.576Z\",\"support\":\"people ignored \"},{\"id\":367,\"lat\":\"51.511207\",\"lng\":\"-0.119225\",\"time\":\"2016-07-14T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Strand\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London\",\"description\":\"I was in Stratford, walking down the streets. My mother sent me to collect something from her friend. I was unable to due to my phone as the battery life was running out \\u0026 switched off all itself. I went to the Lebera phone shop. I asked the retail assistant to charge my phone \\u0026 he did charged it. Then my phone was charged (not fully charged at time as my phone battery life was around 15 to 10%). I called my mother to say that I am not happy with her, sending me out without realising my phone was at low percentage of battery life. I argued with her on the phone and then my phone went goes off again as I recalled moaning. Then suddenly, out of nowhere, the man (white British, who wore brown or grey coat \\u0026 looked middle aged) stuck his noise in a business that does not concern him. He said to me that \\\"this is England, this is Britain, that is not how you talk in this country\\\" I said to the guy in a calm way \\\"that got nothing to do with you sir\\\" then he talked to me rudely \\u0026 harassed me by verbally abusing me, while saying \\\"it's not how you communicate \\u0026 behave in this country, etc\\\". I kept repeating to the person who was racist \\u0026 very rude \\u0026 interfere the business that does not concern. \\\"It has nothing got to do with you sir\\\". He said to me \\\"Don't call me sir\\\". I am black British. I was born in this country the UK \\u0026 I lived here in this country all my life. I never experienced racism before. My parents are from Africa (mum - South African \\u0026 dad - Nigerian).  This is the UK who used to had the biggest empire in the world \\u0026 now victimising the foreigners \\u0026 EU nationals because the whole country voted to leave the European Union.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"Amatare\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-21T23:09:16.605Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T23:31:04.967Z\",\"support\":\"Yes. Someone (caucasian, another word for white) came up to me in a rescue \\u0026 told me \\\"Ignore the man, he is drunk\\\" as he was kind and polite to me. I said \\\"okay\\\" so I ignored the person who was being disrespectful \\u0026 verbally abused me. I walked away \\u0026 the person who was racist to me, walked away too. \"},{\"id\":347,\"lat\":\"52.92253\",\"lng\":\"-1.474619\",\"time\":\"2016-05-22T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Peach street \",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Derby\",\"description\":\"I am a white woman with a mixed race child who I was walking home from the park in the late afternoon, as I turned on to a quiet side-street just a few minutes walk from my home I saw a quite intimidating looking white man. He was tall, lean, bearded and was staring directly into my eyes as he walked my way, obviously travelling in the opposite direction. I was frightened so I looked at the ground and tried to make a plenty of space for the man, I'm ashamed that I allowed myself to be intimidated by this man who I guess was at least 5 years my junior but I am a single mother living in a rather deprived area with nobody to turn to, what could I possibly do?\\r\\n\\r\\nAs he walked on past me, casting a large shadow over me and my daughter he told me in a calm and well spoken manner that my daughter is a 'mongrel'. \\r\\n\\r\\nWe were both upset, our wonderful day had been ruined.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Derby\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-21T15:26:06.503Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T23:41:12.674Z\",\"support\":\"There were two black men walking on the other side of the road when it happened, I'm sure they heard what he said to me and my daughter but they said nothing.\"},{\"id\":366,\"lat\":null,\"lng\":null,\"time\":\"2016-06-02T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Unknown Road\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Lackareagh\",\"description\":\"Me and my family was shocked to witness an incident while we was visiting Ireland. We came over from China and we was having a great time when a man with grey hair did Hitler signs at my family through the window. \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"Co. Clare\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-21T19:05:26.819Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T23:50:12.191Z\",\"support\":\"\"},{\"id\":368,\"lat\":null,\"lng\":null,\"time\":\"2016-07-22T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London\",\"description\":\"Today I was walking down the street when I felt a breeze at the back of my head. I felt for my yarmulke and it was gone.\\r\\n\\r\\nIt had been stolen by some Arab thugs, who taunted me and stamped on my yarmulke. They told me Israel was an illegal country and that I should have been gassed by Hitler. \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":false,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-22T11:58:44.219Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-22T11:58:44.219Z\",\"support\":\"No one offered support or spoke up. I think they supported what those thugs were saying!\"},{\"id\":369,\"lat\":\"51.520261\",\"lng\":\"-0.02934\",\"time\":\"2016-06-16T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"High street tower hamlets\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London Borough of Tower Hamlets\",\"description\":\"I was riding my push bike up the road and a Muslim man approached me saying that I shouldn't be in the area as I was a Jewish man he took my skullcap and set it alight and said that he will burn me in his oven if I ever came back \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":false,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-22T12:12:08.433Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-22T12:12:08.433Z\",\"support\":\"No they did not \"},{\"id\":374,\"lat\":\"51.516263\",\"lng\":\"-0.130662\",\"time\":\"2016-07-22T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Oxford Street\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London\",\"description\":\"I was on the platform of the central line in Tottenham Court Road tube station, and I saw a woman wearing a veil in front of me looking at her shoulder. I noticed it was wet. I asked her was she ok, she said someone spilt alcohol on her. I asked if she thought it might be an accident, she didn't think so. I didn't see the incident but I believe her. I said I was really sorry that happened to her. I wish I had asked her if she wanted to report it. But I was too shocked. I left the station and then returned to report it to staff,\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"W1\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-22T18:35:13.608Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-23T07:53:08.416Z\",\"support\":\"I asked her if she was ok, and we had a brief chat. I also reported it to staff.\"},{\"id\":375,\"lat\":\"51.485093\",\"lng\":\"-0.174936\",\"time\":\"2016-07-22T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Chelsea Manor st\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Royal Borough of Kensington and Chelsea\",\"description\":\"I was walking  down the road with my 4 year old son, talking to him in my native language when this woman in her 50's or 60's stopped in front of us and told us fucking foreigners to go home because \\\"we voted you out.\\\" As I was with my son I wanted to get  out of the situation as quickly as possible, so I just pushed her aside and kept walking. She kept on screaming obscenities after us.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"SW3\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-23T00:03:16.122Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-23T07:53:41.873Z\",\"support\":\"There was no one else around\"},{\"id\":378,\"lat\":\"52.535333\",\"lng\":\"0.826527\",\"time\":\"2016-07-14T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Thetford\",\"description\":\"I'm Polish. Man threw Euro at me and told me 'spend it wisely when you get home'.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"IP24 1PJ\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Norfolk\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-24T18:36:59.423Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-24T2